data.revised_prompt: Generate a professional corporate headshot of an individual. The said individual should be a focused Hispanic male lawyer, shot in photorealistic, studio quality lighting using an 85mm lens, hence giving it a shallow depth of field. The background ought to be neutral grey or present a soft gradient. The lawyer should be dressed in professional attire with accent colors of #008000, appearing confident and approachable with a subtle smile. The composition should be centered with an eye-level camera angle. The lighting should be soft and diffused, with a subtle rim light. The focus needs to be sharply on the eyes, with cinematic color grading. The image should be of 8K resolution, making it ultra-detailed.
